Project Presentation Flow (Starting to Ending)
1. Start With Introduction

Say:

“Good morning everyone.

Today I am going to present my project on Training Institute Management System developed using Django framework.”

2. Tell Project Purpose

Say:

“The main purpose of this project is to manage student information digitally.

This system allows users to register, login, add student records, and view student details easily.”

3. Explain Technologies Used

Say:

“I used the following technologies in this project:

Python
Django Framework
HTML
CSS
JavaScript
SQLite Database”
4. Show Homepage First

From your screenshot, explain:

“This is the homepage of my project.

Here users can see navigation options like Home, Courses, About Us, Login, and Contact.

There is also a registration form where new users can create an account.”

5. Explain Registration Logic

Say:

“When a user fills the registration form, data is sent to Django backend.

The system checks whether username already exists.

If username is unique, user account is created successfully.”

6. Explain Login Module

Say:

“After registration, user can login using username and password.

Django authentication checks credentials.

If login is successful, user is redirected to Add Student page.”

7. Explain Add Student Module

Say:

“Here user can add student details such as:

Name
Age
Description
Student Image

All data is stored in database.”

8. Explain Student List

Say:

“In student list page, all student records are displayed.

Users can also search student by name.”

9. Explain Update & Delete

Say:

“Users can update existing student details and also delete records when required.”

10. Explain Security

Say:

“I used Django authentication and login_required decorator.

This means only logged-in users can access student management pages.”

11. Conclusion

Say:

“This project helps training institutes manage student data efficiently and reduce manual work.

Thank you.”

Best Presentation Order
Introduction
Objective
Technologies
Homepage
Registration
Login
Add Student
Student List
Update/Delete
Conclusion

This flow will make your presentation look confident and organized.